FBIS4-36580 "drnes112_j_94013" FBIS-NES-94-112 Daily Report 10 Jun 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Brahimi Meets U.S., French Ambassadors Brahimi Meets U.S., French Ambassadors JN1006080494 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 0430 GMT 10 Jun 94 JN1006080494 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network Arabic BFN [Text] Brother Lakhdar Brahimi, the UN secretary general's special envoy, yesterday received Arthur Hughes and French Ambassador (Martin Lozel) at his place of residence in the Guest Palace in Sanaa. Brother Najib (?Krizi), the UN spokesman in Yemen, said the meeting came at the request of the two ambassadors within the framework of Brother Lakhdar Brahimi's visit to Yemen to investigate facts in our country for the UN secretary general.
